OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers for
OL,6,Fa time this evening then becoming less
OL,7,Ffrequent overnight, with some clear
OL,8,Fspells developing across the country
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours of the
OL,10,Fmorning. Winds slowly easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,13,Fshowers are still likely in places.
OL,14,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,15,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,16,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
