OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,6,Fat first on Saturday with coastal
OL,7,Fgales possible in South Wales. Rain to
OL,8,Fstart but clearing later. Drier on
OL,9,FSunday though turning wet again
OL,10,Fovernight and into Monday.
